WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 12=
=Crash The Wedding While You Can=

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:03.000
Steven will be here any minute.

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:05.040
But our numbers

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.480
aren't hitting 100% because of

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:07.800
Chen Miaomiao and Hu Yitong.

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:09.880
It's bound to affect
the next round of funding.

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:40.200
You just wanted to toy with me,

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:42.400
didn't you?

00:02:02.080 --> 00:02:02.920
Don't touch me.

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:17.040
An engagement gift.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.600
Don't treat me like this.

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.960
If there's even a shred
of reluctance in you,

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.480
even just a flicker,

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:37.640
then find a way to keep me.

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:39.520
Alright?

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:24.640
Don't worry.

00:03:25.320 --> 00:03:26.400
Even if I have to crash it,

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.400
I won't let them get engaged.

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:31.160
You truly want to marry Ding Daang?

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:33.520
I just need to reach my goal.

00:03:33.890 --> 00:03:34.760
Anything else

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:36.000
doesn't matter to me.

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:38.600
Don't you think that's kind of cold?

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.200
Are you questioning me?

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:10.760
Surprise.

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:14.360
Mr. Steven's schedule changed last minute.

00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:15.940
He asked me to represent him

00:04:15.940 --> 00:04:17.220
as his psychological consultant.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:19.720
I'm here to review the final report

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.440
on the next round of funding
of Keep Love.

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:25.920
President Hu,

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:28.520
you have quite the network.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:31.280
Didn't expect a psychologist like you

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:32.800
to have more than one identity.

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:35.080
I'll walk you through

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:36.440
Keep Love's latest data

00:04:37.480 --> 00:04:39.160
and its growth potential later.

00:04:40.520 --> 00:04:41.360
The data?

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:43.680
President Yu,

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:47.360
numbers can lie.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:50.680
Especially when the core data

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:52.920
has serious flaws.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.000
To be specific,

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.480
a young woman

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:05.720
was used by her own brother

00:05:05.720 --> 00:05:07.000
as a test subject,

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:09.520
but the experiment failed.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:16.000
You plotted against me.

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:19.400
Yu Kun, oh Yu Kun.

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:22.760
Keep Love,
the one you hyped to the skies,

00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:24.960
couldn't even heal

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:25.960
your sister's heart.

00:05:27.320 --> 00:05:28.880
Once the world finds out,

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.560
how will you answer your investors?

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:43.800
By the way,

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:47.400
tomorrow is my engagement party
with Ding Daang.

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:50.920
As her unforgettable ex,

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.080
you really should come.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:57.400
See for yourself

00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:00.080
how a perfect partner

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:01.080
whom you handed to me

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:04.960
becomes mine

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:08.120
right in front of everyone.

00:06:21.540 --> 00:06:24.220
(Joy)

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:33.480
Miss, you look stunning.

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:35.080
On my engagement day,

00:06:35.080 --> 00:06:36.520
I want to wear this dress too.

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:40.000
To get engaged,
you need a boyfriend first.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:44.520
(Aming,)

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.360
(will you show up?)

00:06:58.800 --> 00:06:59.640
Stop overthinking it.

00:07:00.640 --> 00:07:02.120
This is nothing but a gamble.

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:04.360
Whatever the outcome,

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.280
you need to face the truth.

00:07:08.320 --> 00:07:09.520
I admit, I am taking a bet

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:12.520
on the last piece of his sincerity.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.660
He might act on impulse for me once more.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.240
If I win this bet,

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:20.000
there's still a chance for us.

00:07:24.840 --> 00:07:25.680
Alright.

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.840
Whatever you want to do,

00:07:29.360 --> 00:07:31.000
I'll back you up.

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:57.880
Ding Daang.

00:07:58.520 --> 00:07:59.800
The guests are waiting.

00:08:01.240 --> 00:08:02.280
Let's head inside.

00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:09.400
What are you stalling for?

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:10.520
Come on, get in there.

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:12.520
Everyone's waiting for you.

00:08:19.590 --> 00:08:26.950
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:08:28.460 --> 00:08:31.340
Congratulations on your marriage.

00:08:31.400 --> 00:08:33.340
♪They say♪

00:08:37.130 --> 00:08:39.230
The bride is absolutely beautiful.

00:08:41.420 --> 00:08:42.400
Come on, look over here.

00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:45.630
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:08:45.850 --> 00:08:51.800
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:08:53.180 --> 00:08:58.940
♪I've already lost you♪

00:08:58.940 --> 00:09:04.420
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:10.670
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:09:13.400 --> 00:09:14.720
Aming.

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:16.240
Come back.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:20.360
Please, come back.

00:09:22.400 --> 00:09:23.280
Aming.

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:26.360
I don't want to waste time.

00:09:29.840 --> 00:09:31.200
I warned you before.

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:32.480
Stop bringing up the past.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:34.840
Don't call me Chen Aming.

00:09:34.840 --> 00:09:35.880
My name is Yu Kun.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:40.320
You decide for yourself.

00:09:40.910 --> 00:09:43.580
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:46.040
If even a part of you still cares,

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:49.480
then find a way to keep me.

00:10:04.010 --> 00:10:04.870
Once I leave here,

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:06.040
I'll never want to come back.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:11.000
Which city do you want to live in most?

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:11.960
Mancheng.

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:14.320
Mancheng is where we made

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.680
the best memories together.

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:17.760
I want my wedding

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:19.520
to be held at the seaside in Mancheng.

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:21.120
Give me the most romantic

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:22.680
and the most beautiful wedding ever.

00:10:22.680 --> 00:10:23.520
Please?

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:29.360
Well...

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:32.080
Then you need to tell me

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:33.360
what kind of gifts you want.

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:34.640
So I can get them ready.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:39.440
Since you ask,

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:41.280
I'll name everything I want.

00:11:05.300 --> 00:11:08.120
♪That song suddenly started playing♪

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:10.830
♪And I thought of you again♪

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:16.420
♪Even though I swore to the world
we were done♪

00:11:17.430 --> 00:11:19.840
♪All my friends laughed at me♪

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:22.440
I want...

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:27.280
Tong Sui just like this.

00:11:27.280 --> 00:11:28.800
At least ninety-nine bowls of it.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:31.760
♪You keep running through my mind♪

00:11:32.280 --> 00:11:33.200
I hope our love

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.520
can last for a lifetime.

00:11:35.390 --> 00:11:36.440
♪Why♪

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:39.600
♪You walked out of my world♪

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:40.560
Yu Kun.

00:11:41.340 --> 00:11:42.420
What are you trying to do?

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:46.840
I'm here to congratulate my first love

00:11:47.760 --> 00:11:49.280
on her engagement

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:52.120
treat everyone to

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:54.080
Tong Sui, Miss Ding's favorite.

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.080
Ding Daang.

00:12:09.640 --> 00:12:11.000
I kept my promise.

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:13.400
What about you?

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:20.840
Was that slap too much?

00:12:22.160 --> 00:12:24.360
The harder it hits, the faster it works.

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.760
The closure Boss wants

00:12:26.760 --> 00:12:29.080
is never a gentle goodbye.

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:30.720
My Maimai looks so cool.

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:31.560
Right?

00:12:31.600 --> 00:12:33.400
She's unstoppable
when she's protective.

00:12:34.520 --> 00:12:36.120
Being lovesick is like catching a virus.

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:37.840
You should get it fixed soon.

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.280
Are Boss's stats increasing?

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.720
No one's getting married today.

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:46.600
Chen Miaomiao.

00:12:46.960 --> 00:12:47.920
Are you crazy?

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.000
Get out of here!

00:12:49.760 --> 00:12:50.800
Am I the crazy one?

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:52.360
She took everything from me.

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:54.600
Hu Yitong.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:56.560
Do you really think

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:57.760
she's your true love?

00:12:58.120 --> 00:12:58.960
She's a third wheel

00:12:58.960 --> 00:13:00.560
who broke up someone else's relationship.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:05.760
Stop pretending to be innocent.

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:14.040
Who told you to come back?

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:15.560
I told you already,

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.120
I'd take care of it.

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:20.080
Yet you still called off the engagement
for a jerk like me.

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:22.200
That's because I made Aming a promise.

00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:23.920
I'd only marry him in this life.

00:13:24.560 --> 00:13:26.280
I kept my word to him.

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:27.720
But all of this

00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:30.040
has nothing to do with you.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:32.500
Have you asked him what he really wants?

00:13:32.500 --> 00:13:34.080
He just wants to forget the pain.

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:35.120
Why did you get to decide?

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:36.920
If he's suffering, I'd rather he be gone.

00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:39.160
Chen Aming.

00:13:40.040 --> 00:13:41.160
It's been so many years.

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:42.720
You're still holding on.

00:13:44.200 --> 00:13:46.000
You think you can get out of here?

00:14:11.430 --> 00:14:18.430
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:14:22.830 --> 00:14:30.190
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:36.580
♪They say♪

00:14:36.990 --> 00:14:45.370
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:14:45.890 --> 00:14:48.870
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:14:49.090 --> 00:14:55.040
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:14:56.420 --> 00:15:02.180
♪I've already lost you♪

00:15:02.180 --> 00:15:07.660
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:15:07.960 --> 00:15:13.910
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:15:13.910 --> 00:15:18.690
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:15:19.800 --> 00:15:23.830
♪The past will always pass♪

00:15:24.160 --> 00:15:31.740
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:15:32.210 --> 00:15:35.460
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:15:36.020 --> 00:15:41.670
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:15:44.130 --> 00:15:47.660
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:15:47.660 --> 00:15:53.920
♪But sadly, it's not you♪